# 📱 SmartRemind – Intelligent Daily Reminder & Habit Tracker

SmartRemind is a modern iOS productivity application designed to help users efficiently manage daily tasks, habits, and recurring reminders from a single platform.

Built using **SwiftUI**, **Core Data**, and **UserNotifications**, the app provides an intuitive user experience with smart scheduling, habit tracking, template-based reminders, and customizable notifications.

---
