## 🚀 Features

### ✅ Task Management
- Create, edit, and delete tasks
- Priority-based organization
- Due date and time scheduling
- Daily completion tracking

### ✅ Habit Tracking
- Create recurring habits
- Mark habits as completed
- Automatic daily reset
- Progress monitoring

### ✅ Smart Reminder Templates
- Birthday Reminder Templates
- Daily Important Activity Templates
- Quick reminder creation
- Reusable reminder workflows

### ✅ Notification System
- Local notifications
- Repeat alerts (2, 5, and 10-minute intervals)
- Deep-link navigation from notifications
- Priority-based reminder handling

### ✅ Today Dashboard
- Displays all reminders due today
- Completion tracking
- Dynamic filtering
- Clean card-based interface

### ✅ Statistics Dashboard
- Daily completion insights
- Productivity tracking
- Reminder analytics
- Habit performance monitoring

### ✅ User Experience
- Dark Theme Support
- Light Theme Support
- Responsive SwiftUI Design
- Smooth Navigation

### ✅ Offline Support
- Core Data Persistence
- Local Data Storage
- No Internet Required

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|----------|
| Swift | Programming Language |
| SwiftUI | User Interface |
| Core Data | Local Database |
| UserNotifications | Notification Management |
| WidgetKit | Home Screen Widgets |
| MVVM | Architecture Pattern |

---

## 📊 Project Highlights

- Supports **3 reminder types** (Tasks, Habits, Templates)
- Handles **50+ reminders and habits efficiently**
- Provides **100% offline functionality**
- Includes **repeat notification engine**
- Implements **modern SwiftUI architecture**
- Features **Dark and Light Themes**

